_sText: I am adding this map again because an admin deleted the old one I had uploaded.  His reasoning was because the cs_kismayoHDR version was a newer, superior version so it should take the place of cs_kismayo.  This is flawed logic because not every server wants to run the HDR version.  Also, people already have the cs_kismayo version and do not want to switch.  So, I uploaded the map again.  Please do not delete it this time because it has been requested multiple times for me to re upload it.
